"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10020305\">",
"      What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10020300\">",
"      How is this drug best taken?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
